# Faz 12: Security Hardening + Penetration Test

## Goal

Security release gate: 0 HIGH/CRITICAL SAST/SCA/container scan. OWASP ZAP baseline + DAST staging full scan. CSP nonce-based — `unsafe-inline` yok. Secret rotation + backup restore drills staging'de başarılı. 15+ incident runbooks `docs/runbooks/`. Pen-test findings remediated (scope kararı insanın).

Detay: `Docs/10_IMPLEMENTATION_ROADMAP.md` §Faz 12.

**Bağımlılık:** Faz 11 complete; staging prod-parity; OWASP ASVS L3 kritik %80 hedef (`04-quality-gates`).

