infra/                   scan configs, drill scripts
```

### Files NOT touched

- New product features
- Production IaC apply — Faz 13

## Constraints

### Use

- Root cause per security finding
- Nonce-based CSP — no unsafe-inline waiver
- Documented false-positive ignore list (minimal)
- Staging drills before prod
- Human decision on pen-test scope disputes

### Avoid

- Quick-fix without root cause
- unsafe-inline CSP "temporary"
- Agent marking findings out-of-scope without human
- Skip backup restore drill

